{"id":11700,"date":"2021-02-24T10:25:25","date_gmt":"2021-02-24T10:25:25","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/www.valuecoders.com\/blog\/?p=11700"},"modified":"2024-02-16T10:03:03","modified_gmt":"2024-02-16T10:03:03","slug":"web-development-tools-resources","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/www.valuecoders.com\/blog\/technology-and-apps\/web-development-tools-resources\/","title":{"rendered":"Some Essential And Amazing Web Development Tools And Resources"},"content":{"rendered":"<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">The web world is constantly changing. Every day, hundreds of thousands of new websites are added to intensify the competition. According to statistics, the thriving web world has more than 1,800 websites, best UI framework, open-source web development tools, many web development software and to date, less than 200 million active websites.<\/span><\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">In this competitive field, if you want your business website to be visible among all active websites, you must implement innovative ideas, follow development trends and utilize top web development tools. It is inevitable that web developers take into account future trends while developing a business-level website.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><iframe title=\"7 Best Web Development Tools &amp; Resources For Web Developers &amp; Designers | Latest Tools 2019-20\" width=\"640\" height=\"360\" src=\"https:\/\/www.youtube.com\/embed\/f3TyiFCJ7jY?feature=oembed\" frameborder=\"0\" allow=\"accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share\" referrerpolicy=\"strict-origin-when-cross-origin\" allowfullscreen><\/iframe><\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">So, in this blog, I will discuss some amazing web development tools &amp; resources to give your business a good future. However, the web development field is vast. So, I have majorly categorized whole web development software into five parts that are listed below.<\/span><\/p>\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"1_Front-end_web_dev_tools\"><\/span><b>1) Front-end web dev tools<\/b><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-13577\" src=\"https:\/\/www.valuecoders.com\/blog\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/07\/Front-end-developemtn-1.png\" alt=\"front end Web Development tools\" width=\"700\" height=\"350\" srcset=\"https:\/\/www.valuecoders.com\/blog\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/07\/Front-end-developemtn-1.png 700w, https:\/\/www.valuecoders.com\/blog\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/07\/Front-end-developemtn-1-300x150.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 700px) 100vw, 700px\" \/><\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">These web dev tools\/frameworks generally consist of a open-source web development package which consists of other files and folders, such as HTML, CSS, JavasScript, etc. There are also many independent frames out there in this. As we know, a solid web dev tool\/framework can be an essential tool for front-end developers. So must look for such <a href=\"https:\/\/www.valuecoders.com\/blog\/technology-and-apps\/top-software-development-frameworks-tools-and-libraries\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"><strong>top web development tools<\/strong> <strong>list<\/strong><\/a> below:<\/span><\/p>\n<h3 style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"a_Bootstrap\"><\/span><strong>a)\u00a0 <a href=\"https:\/\/getbootstrap.com\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Bootstrap<\/a><\/strong><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">It is a user application framework developed to support the creation of dynamic websites and web applications. It is one of the preferred front-end frameworks, as it helps easy and fast processing to develop a website. It is compatible with all major browsers and fast loading of sensitive web pages.<\/span><\/p>\n<h4 style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>Advantages:<\/strong><\/h4>\n<ol style=\"text-align: justify;\">\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Provide fast development and save your coding efforts<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Ensures ultimate consistency<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Equipped with 12-column grid system and responsive layout<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Helps to fix issues promptly<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Facilitates abundant customization<\/span><\/li>\n<\/ol>\n<p><a href=\"https:\/\/www.valuecoders.com\/hire-developers\/hire-front-end-developers?utm_source=Bgbanner_al&amp;utm_medium=web_tools_11700_rg121&amp;utm_campaign=SMEs\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"size-full wp-image-15307 aligncenter\" src=\"https:\/\/www.valuecoders.com\/blog\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/07\/full-stack-developers.jpg\" alt=\"front-end development\" width=\"810\" height=\"152\" srcset=\"https:\/\/www.valuecoders.com\/blog\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/07\/full-stack-developers.jpg 810w, https:\/\/www.valuecoders.com\/blog\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/07\/full-stack-developers-300x56.jpg 300w, https:\/\/www.valuecoders.com\/blog\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/07\/full-stack-developers-768x144.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 810px) 100vw, 810px\" \/><\/a><\/p>\n<h3 style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"b_Semantic_UI\"><\/span><strong>b) <a href=\"https:\/\/semantic-ui.com\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Semantic UI<\/a><\/strong><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">It is a web development framework that helps create beautiful and sensitive designs using human-friendly HTML. The projects that are built with this web development tool can be incredible, although it is a challenge.\u00a0<\/span><\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">While Bootstrap provides only one basic theme, the semantic user interface includes more than more than 20 themes in its basic package, in addition to CSS, JS and font files. It also includes the Composer, Bower and Gulp configuration files.<\/span><\/p>\n<h4 style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>Advantages:<\/strong><\/h4>\n<ol style=\"text-align: justify;\">\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Create beautiful designs\u00a0<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Provide official support for third party apps<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Offer incredible customization options\u00a0<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Include a ton of UI components for responsive solutions<\/span><\/li>\n<\/ol>\n<h3 style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"c_Foundation\"><\/span><strong>c) <a href=\"https:\/\/foundation.zurb.com\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Foundation<\/a><\/strong><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">It is a user application framework that is a collection of HTML, CSS and JS that contains design patterns on which it can be built. Save time and help web developers write better code. It is a response framework that uses CSS media queries and a mobile approach. In fact, designers can create unique designs for a variety of screen sizes, ensuring a trouble-free experience regardless of the device.<\/span><\/p>\n<h4 style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>Advantages:<\/strong><\/h4>\n<ol style=\"text-align: justify;\">\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Possess a robust grid system<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Offers services for sites as well as emails<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Offers finest of the customization abilities<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Supports a rapid development of projects<\/span><\/li>\n<\/ol>\n<hr \/>\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"2_Databases\"><\/span><b>2) Databases<\/b><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<figure id=\"attachment_11702\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-11702\" style=\"width: 660px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"wp-image-11702 \" src=\"https:\/\/www.valuecoders.com\/blog\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/07\/datri.png\" alt=\"Top web development tools list\" width=\"660\" height=\"330\" srcset=\"https:\/\/www.valuecoders.com\/blog\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/07\/datri.png 750w, https:\/\/www.valuecoders.com\/blog\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/07\/datri-600x300.png 600w, https:\/\/www.valuecoders.com\/blog\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/07\/datri-300x150.png 300w, https:\/\/www.valuecoders.com\/blog\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/07\/datri-640x320.png 640w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 660px) 100vw, 660px\" \/><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-11702\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Source: Google Images<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">A database is the collection of information\/data which is stored. It can be retrieved, updated and managed at anytime.\u00a0<\/span><\/p>\n<h3 style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"a_MySql\"><\/span><strong>a) <a href=\"https:\/\/www.mysql.com\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">MySql<\/a><\/strong><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">It is a free open source database that facilitates the <a href=\"https:\/\/www.devart.com\/dbforge\/mysql\/studio\/database-administration.html\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">effective administration of databases<\/a> by connecting them to the software. It is a stable, reliable and powerful solution with many advanced features.<\/span><\/p>\n<h4 style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>Advantages:<\/strong><\/h4>\n<ol style=\"text-align: justify;\">\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Offer data security and support for transactional processing<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Ensure optimum speed for enhanced performance<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Gives complete workflow control<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Provide flexibility of open-source<\/span><\/li>\n<\/ol>\n<p><a href=\"https:\/\/www.valuecoders.com\/hire-developers\/hire-php-developers?utm_source=Bgbanner_al&amp;utm_medium=web_tools_11700_rg121&amp;utm_campaign=SMEs\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"size-full wp-image-15250 aligncenter\" src=\"https:\/\/www.valuecoders.com\/blog\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/01\/php-developers.jpg\" alt=\"php development\" width=\"810\" height=\"152\" srcset=\"https:\/\/www.valuecoders.com\/blog\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/01\/php-developers.jpg 810w, https:\/\/www.valuecoders.com\/blog\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/01\/php-developers-300x56.jpg 300w, https:\/\/www.valuecoders.com\/blog\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/01\/php-developers-768x144.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 810px) 100vw, 810px\" \/><\/a><\/p>\n<h3 style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"b_PostgreSQL\"><\/span><strong>b) PostgreSQL<\/strong><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">It is an open-source database management system of enterprise class. Supports both SQL for relational and JSON for non-relational queries. It is backed by an experienced community of developers who have made a great contribution to make it a highly reliable <a href=\"https:\/\/learnsql.com\/blog\/what-is-dbms\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">DBMS<\/a> system.<\/span><\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">It supports advanced data types and advanced performance optimization, features only available in the expensive commercial database, such as Oracle and SQL Server.<\/span><\/p>\n<h4 style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>Advantages:<\/strong><\/h4>\n<ol style=\"text-align: justify;\">\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Source code is freely available<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Can run dynamic websites and web apps<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Has a diverse community<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Provide flexible full-text search<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Supports a variety of replication methods<\/span><\/li>\n<\/ol>\n<h3 style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"c_MongoDB\"><\/span><strong>c) <a href=\"https:\/\/www.mongodb.org\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">\u00a0MongoDB<\/a><\/strong><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">It is a popular open source document-oriented database developed by 10gen, later called MongoDB Inc. It is often applied to Node.js. It has attracted considerable consideration with a disseminated key-value store, suitable for calculating MapReduce and document-oriented NoSQL highlights. If you wish to have a high-performing application then an expert and <a href=\"https:\/\/www.valuecoders.com\/dedicated-development-teams\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">dedicated team<\/a> of <strong><a href=\"https:\/\/www.valuecoders.com\/hire-developers\/hire-mean-stack-developers\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">MEAN developers<\/a> or <a href=\"https:\/\/www.valuecoders.com\/hire-developers\/hire-mern-stack-developers\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">MERN developers<\/a> <\/strong>can help you in designing and developing an <a href=\"https:\/\/www.valuecoders.com\/blog\/technology-and-apps\/build-amazing-mobile-app-startup\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">amazing app<\/a> with lot many features and a friendly user interface.<\/span><\/p>\n<h4 style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>Advantages:<\/strong><\/h4>\n<ol style=\"text-align: justify;\">\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Offer many performance advantages<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Has a flexible schema<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Widely used for web applications<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Offers great feature set<\/span><\/li>\n<\/ol>\n<hr \/>\n<h5 style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\">Take A Glance Over: <a href=\"https:\/\/amyrasheldon.medium.com\/top-10-website-development-and-design-trends-to-watch-out-in-2019-6d7f6c281454\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Top 11 Website Development And Design Trends To Watch Out in 2022<\/a><\/span><\/h5>\n<hr \/>\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"3_JavaScript_Libraries\"><\/span><b>3) JavaScript Libraries<\/b><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<figure id=\"attachment_11703\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-11703\" style=\"width: 625px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"wp-image-11703 \" src=\"https:\/\/www.valuecoders.com\/blog\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/07\/javri.jpg\" alt=\"best web development tools\" width=\"625\" height=\"352\" srcset=\"https:\/\/www.valuecoders.com\/blog\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/07\/javri.jpg 778w, https:\/\/www.valuecoders.com\/blog\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/07\/javri-600x338.jpg 600w, https:\/\/www.valuecoders.com\/blog\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/07\/javri-300x169.jpg 300w, https:\/\/www.valuecoders.com\/blog\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/07\/javri-768x432.jpg 768w, https:\/\/www.valuecoders.com\/blog\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/07\/javri-640x360.jpg 640w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 625px) 100vw, 625px\" \/><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-11703\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Source: Google Images<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">JavaScript is one of the most popular programming languages on the web. A JavaScript library is a pre-written JavaScript library that allows easier access during the development of your website or application. For an instance, you can include a copy of the jQuery library hosted by Google using the following code snippet.<\/span><\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">&lt;script src=&#8221;<\/span><a href=\"https:\/\/ajax.googleapis.com\/ajax\/libs\/jquery\/2.2.0\/jquery.min.js\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">https:\/\/ajax.googleapis.com\/ajax\/libs\/jquery\/2.2.0\/jquery.min.js<\/span><\/a><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">&#8220;&gt;&lt;\/script&gt;<\/span><\/p>\n<h3 style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"a_Vuejs\"><\/span><strong>a) <a href=\"https:\/\/vuejs.org\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Vue.js<\/a><\/strong><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">It is a JavaScript library used for building web interfaces with MVVM (Model-View-ViewModel) architecture pattern. It has replaced Ember, Angular and combining modern tooling with supporting libraries to produce a single page application.\u00a0<\/span><\/p>\n<h4 style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>Features:<\/strong><\/h4>\n<ol style=\"text-align: justify;\">\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Flexible<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Good detailed documentation<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Covers drawbacks of ReactJS &amp; AngularJS<\/span><\/li>\n<\/ol>\n<h3 style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"b_Reactjs\"><\/span><strong>b) <a href=\"https:\/\/react.dev\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">React.js<\/a><\/strong><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">React.js is one of those Javascript libraries that has achieved great popularity in the domain of online and web-based businesses, and also for good reason. It has already reached the point of being the mainstream and is used by several large companies. including, of course, Facebook, but Netflix, PayPal, Tesla Motors, Walmart, AirBNB, DropBox, IMDb and many others.<\/span><\/p>\n<h4 style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>Features:<\/strong><\/h4>\n<ol style=\"text-align: justify;\">\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Boosts productivity and facilitates maintenance<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Ensures faster rendering<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">SEO friendly<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Guarantees stable code<\/span><\/li>\n<\/ol>\n<p><a href=\"https:\/\/www.valuecoders.com\/hire-developers\/hire-reactjs-developers?utm_source=Bgbanner_al&amp;utm_me